ubuntu-game-session (0.4) resolute; urgency=medium

  * ubuntu-game-session: only launch Steam in Big Picture / gamepadui mode
    when GDM autologin is active for the current user; manual session
    selection now starts plain Steam.
  * Add new binary package ubuntu-game-desktop: a lightweight Wayland gaming
    desktop (labwc + waybar + wofi) where games are launched via per-game
    gamescope wrappers rather than a gamescope kiosk session. Includes a
    waybar panel with Wi-Fi status/connection editor, battery indicator, app
    launcher, clock, and power controls (logout, reboot, shut down).

 -- Ken VanDine <ken.vandine@canonical.com>  Sat, 21 Jun 2026 15:33:00 -0400

ubuntu-game-session (0.3) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Rename ubuntu-game-autologin to ubuntu-game-handheld.
  * Drop HHD pip/venv/AppImage/udev installation from postinst — HHD is
    now a proper package dependency (Depends: hhd) built from the
    companion ../hhd source package.
  * Simplify ubuntu-game-handheld.postinst: only configure GDM autologin,
    polkit, sudoers, boot session reset service, and enable hhd@user.service.
  * Simplify ubuntu-game-handheld.postrm: remove udev rule and HHD symlink
    cleanup (now owned by the hhd package).
  * State directory renamed to /var/lib/ubuntu-game-handheld.
  * Revert Build-Depends to debhelper-compat + build-essential only.
  * Update standalone setup script to install hhd via apt (with pip fallback).

 -- Ken VanDine <ken.vandine@canonical.com>  Sat, 21 Jun 2026 14:19:00 -0400

ubuntu-game-session (0.2) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Split single package into two binary packages:
    - ubuntu-game-session: core session (gamescope wrapper, desktop entry,
      Steam snap install); suitable for any desktop or laptop.
    - ubuntu-game-autologin: GDM autologin, HHD, boot reset service, polkit
      rule, and desktop shortcut; depends on ubuntu-game-session; intended
      for handheld gaming PCs (Legion Go, Steam Deck, etc.).
  * Switch Steam installation from Valve APT repo to Steam snap.
  * Rename source package from udeck to ubuntu-game-session.
  * State directory renamed to /var/lib/ubuntu-game-autologin.

 -- Ken VanDine <ken.vandine@canonical.com>  Sat, 21 Jun 2026 14:00:00 -0400

ubuntu-game-session (0.1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Rebrand gaming session from "Steam OS" to "Ubuntu Game Session".
  * Rename binaries: steamos-session → ubuntu-game-session,
    steamos-session-select → ubuntu-game-session-select.
  * Rename session desktop file: steamos.desktop → ubuntu-game-session.desktop.
  * Rename systemd service: steamos-autologin-reset → ubuntu-game-session-autologin-reset.
  * Rename sudoers file: steamos-desktop-switch → ubuntu-game-session-switch.
  * Update XDG_SESSION_DESKTOP and XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP env vars accordingly.
  * Update all references in postinst, postrm, scripts, and README.

 -- Ken VanDine <ken.vandine@canonical.com>  Sat, 21 Jun 2026 13:48:00 -0400


